
baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Test server
GET http://localhost:8000


### Upload a document (admin)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/admin/upload
Content-Type: application/json
x-admin-password: xxxxxxxx

{
  "title": "Mathew Ryan — Player Report",
  "type": "player",
  "content": "Mathew Ryan is Australia's first choice goalkeeper.\nHe plays for Real Sociedad in La Liga and is one of the most experienced players in the Socceroos squad.\n\nHis shot stopping is excellent. Strong in one on one situations.\nGood with his feet for a keeper which suits Australia's build up play.\n\nWeakness is dealing with crosses in crowded boxes.\nCan be indecisive when coming off his line under pressure."
}

### Get all documents (admin)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/admin/documents
x-admin-password: socceroos2026

### Query (public)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What are Mathew Ryan's weaknesses?"
}

### Test wrong password
POST http://localhost:8000/api/admin/upload
Content-Type: application/json
x-admin-password: wrongpassword

{
  "title": "Test",
  "type": "player",
  "content": "Test content"
}